OL,11,FTwitter that the chatbot had           
OL,12,Fdrastically improved first response and
OL,13,Fresolution time of customers' queries. 
OL,15,FThe tweet sparked outrage online.      
OL,17,FIt comes at a time when there has been 
OL,18,Fa lot of conversation and apprehension 
OL,19,Fabout AI taking away people's jobs,    
OL,20,Fspecially in the services industry.    
